to college.

03:30.961 --> 03:33.255
I'm a Trojan man myself,
but no judgment.

03:33.297 --> 03:35.883
BILLY: Oh, yeah? How do you know
where she goes to school?

03:35.925 --> 03:37.927
ANTON: Eh, just be careful
what you say to Rita.

03:37.968 --> 03:39.845
Nothing she loves more
than a little bit of keno,

03:39.887 --> 03:41.180
whiskey and some idle gossip.

03:41.221 --> 03:42.890
I'll keep that in mind.

03:43.933 --> 03:46.310
All right.

03:48.854 --> 03:52.441
These... are for your daughter.

03:52.483 --> 03:54.109
And if she's interested,
she could become

03:54.151 --> 03:55.527
a brand ambassador on campus.

03:55.569 --> 03:56.946
It's a paid position,

03:56.987 --> 03:59.448
promoting Blackwood Almond
products at various venues.

03:59.490 --> 04:02.451
It's not too time-consuming,
and the application is online.

04:02.493 --> 04:04.453
Excellent. Well,
I'll make sure and tell her.

04:04.495 --> 04:06.622
- Yeah.
- Have a good day.

04:06.664 --> 04:08.791
Yeah, you, too. Yeah, yeah.
Thanks for the lift.

04:08.832 --> 04:11.377
- Anytime!
- (QUIETLY): Don't know why the fuck you gave it to me

04:11.418 --> 04:13.420
