04:16.757 --> 04:19.969
Hey, listen, uh,
let me ask you a question.

04:20.010 --> 04:22.888
Uh, you know
any dirt roads around here

04:22.930 --> 04:24.473
with, like, a wooden gate?

04:24.515 --> 04:26.725
There's all kinds of dirt roads.
What are you looking for?

04:26.767 --> 04:28.310
Well, last night,
I was walking around.

04:28.352 --> 04:30.896
I saw lights and heard
some drilling going on.

04:30.938 --> 04:32.731
There's a lot of drilling
around here.

04:32.773 --> 04:35.317
- Oh.
- Everyone's trying to dig the deeper well.

04:35.359 --> 04:37.486
Yeah, I hear you.

04:37.528 --> 04:39.321
Back to the casino?

04:39.363 --> 04:40.823
Yes, sir.

