07:45.966 --> 07:48.218
(SKIDDING)

07:49.219 --> 07:51.597
(INSECTS TRILLING)

07:52.598 --> 07:54.975
(MUTTERS)

07:56.101 --> 07:59.062
Fuck.

07:59.104 --> 08:01.481
God.

08:04.693 --> 08:06.987
(GROANS)

08:07.029 --> 08:08.780
Okay.

08:08.822 --> 08:10.782
(EXHALES)

08:10.824 --> 08:13.410
(QUIETLY): AAA.

08:13.452 --> 08:15.871
(MOTORCYCLE APPROACHING)

08:24.671 --> 08:26.632
