Out, get out.

11:44.079 --> 11:45.497
You okay?

11:47.165 --> 11:49.292
Yes.

11:50.961 --> 11:53.797
(GRUNTS)

11:53.839 --> 11:56.633
Hot day for car trouble.

11:56.675 --> 11:58.135
You thirsty?

11:58.176 --> 12:00.554
Thank you.

12:00.595 --> 12:03.098
- Got a spare?
- No.

12:03.140 --> 12:06.309
Shoot, my spare's not
gonna fit your little car.

12:06.351 --> 12:08.311
I'll give you a lift.

12:08.353 --> 12:10.897
Oh, uh... It's okay, the...

12:10.939 --> 12:13.108
Uh, AAA is sending a guy
in, like, two hours.

12:13.150 --> 12:15.861
Girl, I am not leaving you
stranded alone on the road

12:15.902 --> 12:17.779
for a hot-as-hell two hours.

12:17.821 --> 12:20.198
Come on, it's not far.

12:20.240 --> 12:22.159
I'm Violet.

12:22.200 --> 12:24.119
(SIGHS) Violet.

12:24.161 --> 12:26.163
Uh...

12:26.204 --> 12:28.582
Okay, I'm Patty. Hi.

12:30.959 --> 12:32.961
Um...

12:34.588 --> 12:36.298
Do you know where

12:36.339 --> 12:39.718
the Blackwood County
Water Board is?

12:39.759 --> 12:43.263
We have a water board?

12:43.305 --> 12:45.599
I got to do another delivery
before I drop you.

12:45.640 --> 12:47.559
- Hope you don't mind.
- I-I don't have a choice.

12:47.601 --> 12:50.228
- Ha, nope.
- So...

12:50.270 --> 12:51.771
(ENGINE STARTS)

13:09.080 --> 13:10.540
VIOLET: Here we are.

13:15.921 --> 13:19.466
So... how long has this guy
been without water?

13:19.508 --> 13:21.301
- About a year.
- (EXHALES)

13:21.343 --> 13:22.844
- Hey.
- Yeah.

13:22.886 --> 13:24.554
- Grab a case.
- What?

13:24.596 --> 13:27.599
- You got arms, help me out.
- Just... I'll take my seat.

13:27.641 --> 13:30.560
- Hugo.
- Hey, Vi.

13:30.602 --> 13:32.437
This is my new best friend,
Patty.

13:32.479 --> 13:34.231
Nope. We're not best friends.
We're not best friends.

13:34.272 --> 13:36.233
- She's a lawyer from L.A.
- HUGO: Hey.

13:36.274 --> 13:37.984
Any chance I get an extra case?

13:38.026 --> 13:39.402
(GRUNTS) Just three.

13:39.444 --> 13:41.488
Sorry, bud.

13:41.530 --> 13:43.448
- You got it?
- Oh, yeah.

13:43.490 --> 13:45.325
Come on, then.

13:49.204 --> 13:51.414
PATTY: Nothing out of the tap, huh?

13:53.667 --> 13:55.168
Wow.

13:55.210 --> 13:58.547
Backyard well dried up.

13:58.588 --> 14:00.632
Trying to dig a new one
out front.

14:02.092 --> 14:06.763
No toilet water,
nothing for cooking or cleaning.

14:06.805 --> 14:09.307
Can't sell the house 'cause...

14:09.349 --> 14:12.894
who wants to live in a house
without water? (CHUCKLES)

14:12.936 --> 14:15.063
PATTY: So how many people

14:15.105 --> 14:17.107
don't have municipal water?

14:17.148 --> 14:18.942
VIOLET: Whole town, pretty much.

14:18.984 --> 14:20.902
My girlfriend's got water,

14:20.944 --> 14:23.863
but she's in housing owned by
the Blackwood Almond Company.

14:23.905 --> 14:26.866
- Lucky bastards, right?
- I guess.

14:26.908 --> 14:28.952
I got to make one more delivery.

14:28.994 --> 14:30.620
How long is this gonna take?

14:30.662 --> 14:32.038
We're here.

14:53.393 --> 14:55.145
My ex.

14:55.186 --> 14:57.188
Sure.

15:14.247 --> 15:16.249
(ENGINE TURNS OFF)

15:22.339 --> 15:24.549
Something must be up your ass

15:24.591 --> 15:26.676
for you to come
all the way out here.

15:26.718 --> 15:30.430
The only thing up my ass
is your sister's foot.

15:30.472 --> 15:32.349
Oh, yours, too?

15:32.390 --> 15:35.769
I have a source says
she's still drilling.

15:35.810 --> 15:37.937
A source?

15:37.979 --> 15:40.106
(CHUCKLING): Are you working
for the school paper?

15:40.148 --> 15:41.566
I ain't kidding.

15:41.608 --> 15:42.984
Billy McBride was out

15:43.026 --> 15:44.819
at the drilling site last night.

15:44.861 --> 15:46.154
I hear you, Roy.

15:46.196 --> 15:48.448
But, look, that lawyer,

15:48.490 --> 15:50.617
he doesn't know what the fuck
he's looking at.

15:50.659 --> 15:52.494
